snackDescription: Marinela Gansito is a famous Latino snack that children have grown up with. This snack is sort of like a mix between a cookie and a mini cake. It has chocolate, cream, various types of filling, but this one contains strawberry! If you want a good introductory snack into Latino culture, then this is a good option!

Another product by Marinela! This is a very interesting snack when I first tried it. Itâ€™s definitely a hit or miss for some people. It contains plain marshmallow and strawberry-flavored marshmallow; coconut shaving, and strawberry cream on top.

Now, this can be considered a meal on its own right; however, in restaurants, this is usually served as a snack or appetizer. In the image, I cooked those. It contains beef, sweet potatoes, carrots, and various spices to enhance its flavor!
